          h3.mt-5 How can I control cookies on my browser?
          p The process varies per browser. You can manage cookies by visiting the help section of your browser:
          ul
            li: a(href="https://support.google.com/chrome/answer/95647" target="_blank") Chrome
            li: a(href="https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/delete-and-manage-cookies-168dab11-0753-043d-7c16-ede5947fc64d" target="_blank") Edge / Internet Explorer
            li: a(href="https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/enhanced-tracking-protection-firefox-desktop" target="_blank") Firefox
            li: a(href="https://support.apple.com/en-ie/guide/safari/sfri11471/mac" target="_blank") Safari
            li: a(href="https://help.opera.com/en/latest/web-preferences/" target="_blank") Opera

