          ul
            li: a(href="http://www.aboutads.info/choices/" target="_blank") Digital Advertising Alliance
            li: a(href="https://youradchoices.ca/" target="_blank") Digital Advertising Alliance of Canada
            li: a(href="http://www.youronlinechoices.com/" target="_blank") European Interactive Digital Advertising Alliance

          h3.mt-5 Other tracking technologies
          p We may use technologies like web beacons (“tracking pixels” or “clear gifs”) to measure engagement, monitor traffic between pages, and analyze marketing effectiveness. These rely on cookies, so disabling cookies may limit functionality.

          h3.mt-5 Flash cookies / Local Shared Objects
          p Some websites use “Flash Cookies” to store preferences or prevent fraud. You can manage these via:
          ul
            li: a(href="http://www.macromedia.com/support/documentation/en/flashplayer/help/settings_manager07.html" target="_blank") Website Storage Settings Panel
            li: a(href="http://www.macromedia.com/support/documentation/en/flashplayer/help/settings_manager03.html" target="_blank") Global Storage Settings Panel

          h3.mt-5 Targeted advertising
          p Third-party advertisers may place cookies on your device to serve relevant ads. They may collect information about your browsing behavior but not personally identifiable details unless you provide them.

          h3.mt-5 Updates to this policy
          p We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time to reflect changes in technology, legal requirements, or our practices. Please revisit this page periodically.

